column4: Metokur seems to have picked up on Tito.
i guarantee you this is part of Metokur's research for his upcoming Maddox video. Hope Maddie's ready for the imminent flamethrower that's about to hit him in the face
Incoming spergout. 5 bucks Dr high class lady esq weighs in
he talked about it on the killstream, he's looking into it.

I was one of the people to call out Tito incessantly early on, but I never thought he'd just keep digging in and eventually become a staple lolcow.  I have a shitload of PMs from him I've never even checked, let alone posted anywhere.

I'm not a Twitter, but this archive-link (his original pedo thread on Reddit, since his account got nuked) might be interesting: http://archive.is/h5NXqIf somebody wants to throw this at Metokur be my guest.

I hope it is. I am genuinely shocked that Metokur hasn't yet made a new video about Maddox. So many lols to mine from the goss saga, and yet still only one video dedicated to the filling of the lolsuit.
I think he was waiting for a definitive end.
If he waits for it to end, he would have to make 10 videos back to back. Better cover the saga as it unfolds, in my opinion.
